                            vol. 7 (1890–97), 1–192.</bibl>
                        <bibl>S. P.  Brock, ‘Saints in Syriac: A little tapped resource’, <title rend="italic"> 
                        <abbr>JECS</abbr>
                            </title> 16 (2008), 181–96, esp. 190–96.</bibl>
                        <bibl>E. A. W.  Budge, <title rend="italic">The Book of Paradise</title> (2
